  🧠 I[0m[2m have examined[0m[2m the current[0m[2m implementation[0m[2m of the[0m[2m checkout process[0m[2m. There[0m[2m are two[0m[2m very[0m[2m obvious[0m[2m race conditions[0m[2m that perfectly[0m[2m explain the[0m[2m symptoms[0m[2m described:[0m[2m "[0m[2mghost charges[0m[2m" and[0m[2m "overs[0m[2melling".[0m[2m
     
     **[0m[2m1[0m[2m. The[0m[2m Ghost Charge[0m[2m Race[0m[2m Condition:**[0m[2m
     In[0m[2m `checkout[0m[2m.py`,[0m[2m the logic[0m[2m is:[0m[2m `check[0m[2m_stock`[0m[2m →[0m[2m `charge[0m[2m` →[0m[2m `de[0m[2mcrement`.[0m[2m
