     **[0m[2m2.[0m[2m The Overs[0m[2melling Race[0m[2m Condition:**[0m[2m
     Wait[0m[2m, there's[0m[2m a[0m[2m second layer[0m[2m here[0m[2m. Look[0m[2m at the[0m[2m `Inventory[0m[2m` class[0m[2m in[0m[2m `inventory[0m[2m.py`.[0m[2m It[0m[2m uses `[0m[2mcheck_stock[0m[2m` and[0m[2m `de[0m[2mcrement`[0m[2m as two[0m[2m separate async[0m[2m calls[0m[2m. Even[0m[2m if we[0m[2m fix[0m[2m the ghost[0m[2m charge,[0m[2m overs[0m[2melling can[0m[2m still happen[0m[2m if[0m[2m two[0m[2m threads[0m[2m call[0m[2m `check[0m[2m_stock`[0m[2m at the[0m[2m same[0m[2m mill[0m[2misecond.[0m[2m They[0m[2m both see[0m[2m `[0m[2mstock >=[0m[2m 1[0m[2m`.[0m[2m Then[0m[2m they both[0m[2m call `[0m[2mdecrement[0m[2m`[0m[2m in[0m[2m quick[0m[2m succession.[0m[2m If[0m[2m the[0m[2m internal[0m[2m state[0m[2m isn't locked[0m[2m or[0m[2m checked[0m[2m atomically[0m[2m, we[0m[2m could[0m[2m end[0m[2m up with[0m[2m a[0m[2m negative number[0m[2m or[0m[2m,[0m[2m more[0m[2m likely,[0m[2m sell[0m[2m one[0m[2m item twice[0m[2m.[0m[2m 
     
     Actually[0m[2m, let's[0m[2m look at[0m[2m the[0m[2m requirements[0m[2m again.[0m[2m The[0m[2m user says[0m[2m to[0m[2m fix the[0m[2m checkout logic[0m[2m and[0m[2m that[0m[2m the[0m[2m test[0m[2m simulation[0m[2m is run[0m[2m via[0m[2m `main[0m[2m.py`.[0m[2m This[0m[2m suggests[0m[2m that[0m[2m the[0m[2m `checkout[0m[2m.py[0m[2m` function[0m[2m needs[0m[2m to be[0m[2m the orchestr[0m[2mator of[0m[2m safety[0m[2m,[0m[2m rather[0m[2m than relying[0m[2m on the[0m[2m `Inventory[0m[2m` or[0m[2m `Payment[0m[2mGateway`[0m[2m classes[0m[2m to handle[0m[2m their own[0m[2m atomic[0m[2mity ([0m[2msince[0m[2m they might[0m[2m not[0m[2m have[0m[2m the full[0m[2m context of[0m[2m the transaction[0m[2m).
     
